h2(#description). Description


The DefaultTag is the base plugin for all tag plugins. It provides the functionality for specifying
which tag names should be handled, methods for setting the configuration and so on.


h2(#about-tags). About Tags


Tags are used to include dynamic content in page files. For more information, have a look at
{plugin: Core/TagProcessor}.

Each tag plugin responds to one or more tag names and creates content dynamically. webgen comes with
a broad range of tag plugins for

* generating menus and breadcrumb trails
* including files
* generating sitemaps
* and much more!
